data.description: This beautiful brick contemporary conveniently located near NAS Pensacola and Perdido Key is PRICED TO SELL! This move-in ready, four bedroom, two bath home has everything you’re looking for. Spacious and open, the floorplan offers flexibility with two main living spaces on either side of the kitchen. Soaring vaulted ceilings with plant ledge details and numerous windows make the rooms feel extra spacious and bright, and luxury vinyl plank flooring runs throughout connecting the common areas. The open kitchen features gorgeous granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, plus a long breakfast bar for casual dining. Split from the additional bedrooms near the back of the home, the master bedroom is totally private. It offers a large walk-in closet and an ensuite bath with double vanity, shower and garden tub, and a water closet. The other three bedrooms run down a separate hallway giving ample privacy for other family members' bedrooms, an office space, etc. Plenty of extra storage can be found in the utility room and the two car garage, which has space for all of your toys and parking needs. Out back is a fully privacy fenced yard and an open patio perfect for grilling on football weekends! Roof was replaced in 2021 so this home is totally turn key!!
